description:

Ballots that are listed as exhausted, spoiled, or otherwise inactive in the winning round will not be included.

The market will resolve to “Under 1%” if the margin is less than 1%, or “1% to 2%” if the margin is between 1% and 2% inclusive, or “Over 2%” if the margin is more than 2%.
